# hey, i'm insyri :wave:

I am a highschool student, self-taught computer programmer and a computer science passionate who resides in Florida, US. I only push to GitHub once I've made a significant progress to a project, that is why I may seem not-so-active on here, but most of my projects are private anyways and once I finish them, they will be made public. I also use GitHub as my pastebin and Google Docs replacement, usually in private gists, but some of them are public. As you could tell, I am a computer science passionate.
